Standard Chartered to Keep Hiring in 2012 and Beyond, CEO Says

-- B y   S t e p h a n i e   T o n g
-- 
2011-09-30T02:44:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/standard-chartered-to-keep-hiring-in-2012-and-beyond-ceo-says.html
Standard Chartered Plc (STAN)  will
continue to hire in 2012 and beyond, Chief Executive Officer
 Peter Sands  told reporters in  Hong Kong  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
